		"description": "<p><em><strong>Target:</strong> One hammer that you are holding</em></p>\n<p>You magically imbue a hammer to strike harder and faster. When cast on a mundane hammer or smithing hammer, the metal of the hammer&rsquo;s head becomes magically reinforced, allowing it to work more efficiently. You gain an expertise die on checks made to craft or repair items that would require the use of a hammer.</p>\n<p>When this spell is cast on a light hammer or warhammer, the weapon deals an additional 2d6 force damage for its duration.</p>\n<p><strong>Cast at Higher Levels.</strong> The damage increases by 1d6 for every spell slot above 2nd.</p>",
